
    <html>
    
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
        <title>My Nature Explorer Page</title>
    
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    </head>
    
    <body>
    
        <!-- container-fluid: full-width header -->
        <div class="container-fluid bg-success text-white p-4">
            <h1>My Nature Explorer Page</h1>
            <p>Explore forests, rivers, mountains, and wildlife through this nature-themed webpage.</p>
        </div>
    
        <!-- container: keeps content centered and neat -->
        <div class="container">
    
            <!-- my-3: adds vertical spacing, p-3: adds padding -->
            <div class="bg-info text-white p-3 my-3 border border-dark">
                <h2>Forest Adventure</h2>
                <p>
                    Forests are full of trees, animals, birds, and fresh air. They help keep our planet healthy.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="bg-primary text-white p-3 my-3 border border-dark">
                <h2>River Journey</h2>
                <p>
                    Rivers provide water for people, plants, and animals. They also make beautiful natural landscapes.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="bg-warning p-3 my-3 border border-dark">
                <h2>Mountain View</h2>
                <p>
                    Mountains are tall landforms that give us amazing views and are home to many unique plants and animals.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="bg-danger text-white p-3 my-3 border border-dark">
                <h2>Wildlife Zone</h2>
                <p>
                    Wildlife includes animals living freely in nature. We should protect their homes and keep nature safe.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="bg-light p-3 my-3 border border-success">
                <h2>Nature Explorer Checklist</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Observe plants carefully</li>
                    <li>Do not disturb animals</li>
                    <li>Keep the environment clean</li>
                    <li>Carry a water bottle</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
    
        </div>
    
        <!-- container-fluid: full-width footer -->
        <div class="container-fluid bg-dark text-white p-3 my-3">
            <p>Nature Tip: Protecting nature means protecting our future.</p>
        </div>
    
    </body>
    
    </html>